{"tid":2125342,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美又抓到中國間諜！新加坡男「坦承為中蒐集情報」","createTime":"2020-07-26T06:36:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-27T20:11:16.000Z","uid":113000,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"6a77f40f4daf4f1f07e0e9d0084c8d1d416081b6","tid":2125342,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T06:36:40.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕美國司法部24日宣布，有一名新加坡公民承認為中國情報部門蒐集情報，美國司法部助理部長德默斯（John C. Demers）譴責中國，利用美國社會開放性獲取敏感訊息。<br />\n<br />\n《美國之音》報導，該名新加坡人名為楊俊偉（譯音，Jun Wei Yeo，英文名Dickson Yeo），他坦承自己在新加坡國立大學擔任學者時，被中國情報部門招募，指示他設立一個政治諮詢公司，招募了擁有安全許可的美國軍方或政府人員，其中包括空軍F-35B隱形戰鬥轟炸機項目的文職人員、有阿富汗經驗的五角大廈軍官、國務院官員，他們為該公司撰寫報告可以得到2000美元（約台幣58901元）的報酬。<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，楊俊偉承認自己在2015年至2019年間替中國情報部門工作，並在2019年進入美國時被捕，美方對楊的判決將於今年10月決定，最高處10年監禁。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3239236\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3239236&d=OqPbpPrVkTbcBhMc%2F4HaLhZmCTjK%2FM6Kxb2TK%2FvXQ0I%3D&h=3a85e5e5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3239236&h=f3bdb003\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3239236</a>"},{"pid":"237b23c9cbcf5e0e10049745dcee80c4c3069ad5","tid":2125342,"uid":113000,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T06:37:18.000Z","msg":"二次投胎都要走去做間諜<br />\n係咪痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75253b680f8f2623f44afac5b97044360f1cd60e","tid":2125342,"uid":21545,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T06:38:04.000Z","msg":"MSMD<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />btw ho ching 都好可疑"},{"pid":"1564374c3d748d33a1afe6ad632da10b0d284cef","tid":2125342,"uid":121076,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"237b23c9cbcf5e0e10049745dcee80c4c3069ad5","tid":2125342,"uid":113000,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"rep